Marion's Thailand - Season 1, Episode 3




Seafood

Today's ep is all about the food of the sea: fish. Marion starts the day on the beach at Pran Buri in the province of Prachuap Khiri Khan -- where she watches the fishing trawlers come in before BBQing fresh prawns and squid to serve with a spicy Nahm Jim Sauce.




Rebroadcast Air Date: 17-May-2014
